====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|nautical|lang=en}} A [[triangular]] [[staysail]] set forward of the [[foremast]]. In a [[sloop]] (see image) the basic '''jib''' reaches back roughly to the level of the mast.
# {{context|nautical|lang=en}} Usually with a modifier, any of a variety of specialty triangular staysails set forward of the foremast.
# The projecting arm of a [[crane]]
# {{context|metonymy|lang=en}} A [[crane]] used for mounting and moving a [[video camera]]
# An object that is used for performing tricks while [[skiing]], [[snowboarding]], [[skateboarding]], [[inline skating]], or [[biking]].  These objects are usually found in a [[terrain park]] or [[skate park]].

